Tapestry5 Demo Application

Presented at the Macedonia JUG tech meetup at 08.02.2012

http://jug.mk/events/technical2012/

The demo can be seen live and running here: http://tapestrydemoapp.herokuapp.com/

The demo consists of a single page Employees demonstrating basic CRUD functionality.

